### Product Discovery APIs

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/v1

### 1. Get Featured Products (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Featured Products with Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?limit=8
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Featured Products by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?category=hiring&limit=6
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Featured Products by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?type=prompt&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Featured Products with High Rating Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?minRating=4.0&limit=8
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get Featured Products (Prompts Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?type=prompt&category=hiring&limit=12
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get Trending Products (Default - Last 7 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/trending
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get Trending Products (Last 14 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/trending?days=14&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Get Trending Products (Last 30 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/trending?days=30&limit=12
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get High Rated Products (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/high-rated
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Get High Rated Products with Custom Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/high-rated?limit=10&minReviews=5
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Get Recently Added Products (Default - Last 30 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/recently-added
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. Get Recently Added Products (Last 7 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/recently-added?days=7&limit=8
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. Get Recently Added Products (Last 60 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/recently-added?days=60&limit=15
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. Get Complete Product Discovery (All Sections)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/discovery
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. Get Product Discovery for Homepage
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/discovery
Content-Type: application/json

### 17. Test Featured Products Algorithm Edge Cases

# Empty results test
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?category=nonexistent
Content-Type: application/json

### 18. Test Trending Products Edge Cases

# Very short period
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/trending?days=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

### 19. Test High Rated Products Edge Cases

# Very high minimum reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/high-rated?minReviews=100&limit=3
Content-Type: application/json

### 20. Test Recently Added Edge Cases

# Very recent only
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/recently-added?days=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

